        <title type="html"><![CDATA[LG생활건강, MZ 픽 브랜드 ‘힌스’ 425억에 인수]]></title>
        <id>https://www.notion.so/274a1a26f9b14b509cbd6f418313f107?v=1a6d3c03236342a89d7e34cd379f709f</id>
